s-hold-after-beijing-warns-against-targeted-provocation?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>金门防卫司令部原定于周二开始演习，但因天气恶劣而推迟。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 13:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3257570/taiwan-puts-quemoy-live-fire-drills-hold-after-beijing-warns-against-targeted-provocation?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>尽管国有银行面临提高利润的压力，但中国建设银行仍看到北京方面的更多政策支持</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3257609/china-construction-bank-sees-more-policy-support-beijing-despite-pressure-state-owned-lenders-boost?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>建行首席财务官盛六荣表示，中国金融监管机构可能会继续降低融资成本，以此提振信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3257609/china-construction-bank-sees-more-policy-support-beijing-despite-pressure-state-owned-lenders-boost?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国智能手机巨头小米预计首款电动汽车需求强劲，尽管买家面临超过 5 个月的交货等待时间</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3257587/chinese-smartphone-giant-xiaomi-sees-robust-demand-first-ev-even-buyers-face-delivery-wait-times?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>截至周二，小米已锁定 SU7 约 4 万份订单。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:30:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3257587/chinese-smartphone-giant-xiaomi-sees-robust-demand-first-ev-even-buyers-face-delivery-wait-times?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>最高反腐机构称，中国前司法部长唐一军面临腐败调查</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3257603/chinas-former-justice-minister-tang-yijun-facing-corruption-probe-top-anti-graft-agency-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>反腐机构称唐“涉嫌严重违纪违法”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3257603/chinas-former-justice-minister-tang-yijun-facing-corruption-probe-top-anti-graft-agency-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国中小企业制造业小幅增长，​​但尚未表现出“强劲反弹趋势”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3257579/chinas-smes-match-modest-manufacturing-gains-yet-show-strong-rebound-trend?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>对中国私营部门中小型企业进行调查的商业状况指数从2月份的51.6上升至3月份的52.1，与上个月制造业活动的小幅增长相呼应。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3257579/chinas-smes-match-modest-manufacturing-gains-yet-show-strong-rebound-trend?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责以色列袭击伊朗驻叙利亚领事馆</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257605/china-joins-chorus-condemnation-over-israeli-attack-iranian-consulate-syria?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>叙利亚首都大马士革外交建筑遇袭后，北京表示“外交机构的安全不容侵犯”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 11:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257605/china-joins-chorus-condemnation-over-israeli-attack-iranian-consulate-syria?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>马英九呼吁台海两岸共同努力“避免战争”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3257575/ma-ying-jeou-calls-both-sides-taiwan-strait-work-together-and-avoid-war?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>台湾前总统在大陆访问的第二天在孙中山故居发表讲话。在参观了大疆科技和腾讯之后，他周二还与北京官员一起参观了比亚迪汽车总部。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 10:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3257575/ma-ying-jeou-calls-both-sides-taiwan-strait-work-together-and-avoid-war?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“新思维方式”：中国研究人员推出独特的组织再生、功能策略</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3257567/new-way-thinking-chinese-researchers-unveil-unique-strategy-tissue-regeneration-function?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>科学家表示，含有神经干细胞的微型植入物可以在神经的帮助下修复和再生组织和骨骼。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 09:11:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3257567/new-way-thinking-chinese-researchers-unveil-unique-strategy-tissue-regeneration-function?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>雷·达里奥表示，随着北京努力重振经济，现在是买入“廉价”中国股票的时候了</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/markets/article/3257534/ray-dalio-says-now-time-buy-cheap-chinese-stocks-beijing-works-revive-economy?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>这位对冲基金亿万富翁在他的LinkedIn博客中表示，“当每个人都讨厌市场且价格便宜时，就是买入的时机，中国股市现在就是这种情况”，特别是有迹象表明该国经济领导人正在准备刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 06:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/markets/article/3257534/ray-dalio-says-now-time-buy-cheap-chinese-stocks-beijing-works-revive-economy?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>南海：海事专家表示，由于缺乏信任和动力，有争议航道规则书的编写被推迟</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257527/south-china-sea-writing-rule-book-disputed-waterway-delayed-lack-trust-and-momentum-says-maritime?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国南海研究院院长吴士存对南海行为准则的进展感到悲观。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 06:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257527/south-china-sea-writing-rule-book-disputed-waterway-delayed-lack-trust-and-momentum-says-maritime?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>研究发现中国大陆、七国集团对台湾升级的反应将损害各方</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3257505/mainland-china-g7-responses-taiwan-escalation-would-harm-all-parties-research-finds?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>研究人员公布了他们的研究结果，如果台湾问题的紧张局势恶化，七国集团国家和中国大陆可能会采取毁灭性的应对措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:01:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3257505/mainland-china-g7-responses-taiwan-escalation-would-harm-all-parties-research-finds?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>战斗仍在继续，中国军队将在缅甸边境举行实弹演习</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3257477/chinas-military-hold-li